  "subject": "Add playwright e2e tests",
  "commit_message": "Add playwright e2e tests\n\n- define playwright tests in e2e folder\n- remove protractor\n- add e2e/compose folder that contains docker-compose.yaml [0]\n- add e2e/wiremock folder that contains wiremock stubs\n- pin newer versions of GHA\n\n[0] The compose file contains keycloak and a keycloak-config-cli to import\n    an onap realm with the portal-app client.\n    It will also spin up the wiremock that is defined in e2e/wiremock\n\nIssue-ID: PORTALNG-159\nChange-Id: I5f85fb29ec4840ba053fc3a4b2a6828e1f8572f0\nSigned-off-by: Fiete Ostkamp <fiete.ostkamp@telekom.de>\n",
